welcome_message_body: "Welcome to Murphy, the charming city known for its beautiful scenery and friendly locals. We hope you enjoy your stay and take the time to explore all that our lovely city has to offer."

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Love Field Airport serves both domestic and international flights.

terminals.name: Southwest Terminal
terminals.description: The Southwest Terminal at Love Field Airport is dedicated to Southwest Airlines flights.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Terminal A
terminals.description: The largest terminal at DFW, serving domestic and international flights.

terminals.name: Terminal B
terminals.description: A smaller terminal, mainly serving domestic flights.

terminals.name: Terminal C
terminals.description: A busy terminal, mainly serving domestic and international flights.

terminals.name: Terminal D
terminals.description: The international terminal at DFW, serving flights from around the world.

terminals.name: Terminal E
terminals.description: A newer terminal, mainly serving domestic and international flights.

terminals.name: Terminal F
terminals.description: The newest terminal at DFW, mainly serving domestic and international flights.

wifi.note: Free Wi-Fi is available throughout the airport. Premium Wi-Fi is also available for purchase.
